titles.title: Providing for an adjournment of the House from Wednesday, January 27, 1993 to Tuesday, February 2, 1993.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

action.text: Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.

vote.text: Received in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment by Voice Vote.

bill.summary: 1/27/1993--Introduced. Provides for an adjournment of the House of Representatives from January 27, 1993, until February 2, 1993.
